913
00:41:30,500 --> 00:41:31,500
Ten years ago,

914
00:41:31,980 --> 00:41:33,580
His Lordship had a craftsman

915
00:41:34,140 --> 00:41:35,660
make each of us a miniature

916
00:41:35,730 --> 00:41:37,920
golden version of our weapons.

917
00:41:39,140 --> 00:41:40,620
Mine is a small gold dart.

918
00:41:41,620 --> 00:41:42,500
Wei Qu's is

919
00:41:43,300 --> 00:41:44,540
a pair of long and short swords.

920
00:41:45,420 --> 00:41:46,380
Wei Xiao's,

921
00:41:46,940 --> 00:41:48,180
a small gold bow.

922
00:41:48,810 --> 00:41:49,700
Wei Duo's,

923
00:41:49,780 --> 00:41:50,900
a small sword.

924
00:41:52,140 --> 00:41:53,860
I'm not interested

925
00:41:53,860 --> 00:41:55,060
in your man stuff.

926
00:41:56,700 --> 00:41:58,460
To us four,

927
00:41:58,500 --> 00:41:59,580
these miniature weapons

928
00:41:59,860 --> 00:42:01,060
represent who we are.

929
00:42:02,300 --> 00:42:03,660
Every time we go to the battle,

930
00:42:04,540 --> 00:42:06,620
