931
00:42:07,940 --> 00:42:10,540
We weren't born on the same day,

932
00:42:11,340 --> 00:42:12,460
and I guess

933
00:42:12,460 --> 00:42:14,500
we won't die on the same day either.

934
00:42:16,180 --> 00:42:17,060
But one day,

935
00:42:17,500 --> 00:42:19,140
even if all four of us are gone,

936
00:42:20,420 --> 00:42:22,060
burying these miniature weapons together

937
00:42:22,940 --> 00:42:24,500
will mean we'll always be brothers.

938
00:42:28,060 --> 00:42:28,940
So,

939
00:42:32,540 --> 00:42:34,140
I want you to have this.

